lead_paragraph: State lawmakers rejected efforts to expand the state Medicaid program to give the working poor government-funded health insurance, the third year of defeats for the legislation.

headline.print_headline: Louisiana: Lawmakers Refuse to Add More Working Poor to Medicaid
